  <section class="speech-text-column">
      <a href="/the-presidency/presidential-speeches/june-3-1984-remarks-citizens-ballyporeen-ireland" hreflang="en">June 3, 1984: Remarks to the Citizens of Ballyporeen, Ireland</a>
